                    {
                      "id": "c868fca",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p> This system focuses on planting Vetiver strategically in specific locations to create natural barriers that prevent land degradation and soil erosion.</p><p><b>The benefits </b></p><ol><li><p><strong>Incredible Resilience:</strong> Vetiver thrives in various soil types and environments, showcasing its adaptability in the face of different weather conditions. Whether your land is subjected to heavy rainfall or drought, Vetiver remains a reliable solution for soil protection.</p></li><li><p><strong>Cost-Efficiency:</strong> Implementing large-scale greening and land regeneration projects often comes with substantial costs and complexities. The Vetiver System stands out by significantly reducing these costs, with savings of nearly 85% compared to traditional methods, while delivering results of equivalent or even superior quality.</p></li><li><p><strong>Low Maintenance:</strong> Once implemented, the Vetiver System requires minimal maintenance. It is a sustainable solution that keeps working without the need for constant human intervention. This low-maintenance aspect makes it a cost-effective and hassle-free choice for sustainable land management.</p></li></ol>",
                        "align": "justify",
