                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "id": "58cbf96",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "title": "Why use Vetiver",
                        "align": "center",
                        "_margin": {
                          "unit": "px",
                          "top": "18",
                          "right": "18",
                          "bottom": "18",
                          "left": "18",
                          "isLinked": true
                        }
                      },
                      "elements": [],
                      "widgetType": "heading"
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "089ac0a",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p>The Vetiver System doesn't just prevent land degradation; it actively regenerates soils. Here are some of the key advantages:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Soil Stabilization:</strong> Vetiver's deep and extensive root system acts as a natural soil stabilizer, preventing erosion and landslides. It enhances soil structure, making it more resistant to erosion caused by heavy rainfall.</p></li><li><p><strong>Water Flow Reduction:</strong> By strategically planting Vetiver, the Vetiver System can significantly reduce water flows and control runoff. This is vital for preventing soil erosion, conserving water resources, and maintaining ecological balance.</p></li><li><p><strong>Biodiversity Support:</strong> The growth of Vetiver also fosters biodiversity, attracting microorganisms with its unique scent and providing an environment for various species to thrive.</p></li><li><p><strong>Sustainable Land Management:</strong> The Vetiver System offers an eco-friendly and sustainable approach to land management, ensuring that your land remains fertile and productive over the long term.</p></li></ul>",
                        "align": "justify",
                        "_margin": {
                          "unit": "px",
                          "top": "10",
                          "right": "10",
                          "bottom": "10",
                          "left": "10",
                          "isLinked": true
                        },
                        "_padding": {
                          "unit": "px",
                          "top": "15",
                          "right": "15",
                          "bottom": "15",
                          "left": "15",
                          "isLinked": true
                        }
                      },
                      "elements": [],
                      "widgetType": "text-editor"
                    }
                  ],
                  "isInner": true
