          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "1c7fd65",
              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Incorporating the Vetiver System into land management projects brings a host of benefits. Not only does it protect your land from degradation, but it also promotes ecological harmony, reduces costs, and ensures the longevity of your environmental initiatives.</p><p>At Vetiver Sans Frontieres, we're passionate advocates of the Vetiver System. Our mission revolves around empowering communities to rejuvenate their soil using the remarkable properties of Vetiver grass. We invite you to explore the endless possibilities that the Vetiver System offers and join us in our journey to regenerate the world, one plant at a time. Together, we can make a significant impact on sustainable land management and ecological preservation.</p><p><strong>Learn More</strong></p><p>Ready to dive deeper into the Vetiver System and how it can transform your land management initiatives? We encourage you to visit and follow <a href=\"https://www.vetiver.org/vetiver-grass-technology/\"> The Vetiver Network International</a></p>",
                "_margin": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "top": "10",
                  "right": "10",
                  "bottom": "10",
                  "left": "10",
                  "isLinked": true
                },
